data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 1.5-story home with southern charm. Kitchen offers corian countertops, eat-at-bar, dining area and stainless steel appliances including refrigerator. Cozy living room has a fireplace with gas logs. Primary suite on main level includes updated bathroom with tiled shower. The additional bedrooms are spacious and versatile, ideal for a growing family, guests, or a home office.  Entertain with ease in the screened-in porch, complete with a charming swing—perfect for lazy afternoons or lively gatherings. The outdoor space extends to a fenced in back yard that is perfect for the kids or pets. The 24x20 building, heated and cooled, adds an extra layer of convenience and versatility, whether used as a workshop or a mancave. The location of this home is incredibly convenient to shopping and major highways, while being situated on a dead-end street.
